Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.27,0:00:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The cherry blossom is cascaded,\Nsurrounding me and my broken heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.76,0:00:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,In the rain of dancing petals,\NI cried, always alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.56,0:00:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The gentle warmth of sun in the spring,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.61,0:00:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,summer's light through the trees,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the bright glow of autumn\Nthrough cloudy skies,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the morning sun on winter's snow…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.91,0:00:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No trace of light ever found\Nits way to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.96,0:00:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Happiness felt like a cruelty,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.80,0:00:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,always beyond my reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.05,0:00:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Every brief hope would vanish\Nbefore my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.86,0:00:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It all felt so meaningless…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.48,0:00:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If this was the person I was destined\Nto be, why was I born at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:01:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But everything changed when I met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,EPISODE 1\NTHE MEETING
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.72,0:01:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.72,0:01:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bitter! You brewed it for too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.97,0:01:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Your apology means nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo, how long do you intend\Nto stay down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.47,0:01:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Go and re-brew it at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.53,0:01:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness!\NShe can't even make tea properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a Saimori like me,\Nso shouldn't she at least be embarrassed?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a wonder that incompetent girl shares\Nany relation to you, Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.62,0:02:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like that wretched mother of hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.75,0:02:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanoko, please darling, don't blame me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.25,0:02:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one\Nwho made that woman give birth to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.68,0:02:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The past is dead and gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.93,0:02:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we let it stay that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning to you,\NMr. Tatsuishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.39,0:02:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,To what do we owe the pleasure today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.52,0:02:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm meeting with Shinichi\Nto discuss a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,These are for the servants. Please enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.15,0:02:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! We do always appreciate\Nyour generosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! Now, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that\NMr. Tatsuishi arrived a little bit ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he's here\Nto make marriage arrangements
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-for the young ladies?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.05,0:02:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It would make sense as both Miss Miyo\Nand Miss Kaya are around that age.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And Miss Miyo is already 19 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.05,0:02:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She is.\NBut her Master isn't concerned, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.89,0:02:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sad,\Nbut Miss Miyo doesn't really count.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:03:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are your mouths moving\Ninstead of your hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.06,0:03:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you're supposed\Nto be doing the laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.35,0:03:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to work or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-Uh, my apologies, madam.\N-My apologies, madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladies, can someone come\Nto the living room?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, our Madam is calling for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.07,0:03:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes, ma'am, right away!\N-Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Koji… Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tending to the yard again, Miyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hard work shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Koji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Our fathers are having\Nsome important meeting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The plants you have here are so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. We're happy to have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, um… I, I, uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.98,0:03:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked to join him\Nbecause I was hoping we'd get to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:03:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, put your hand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They're milk caramels. It's a chewy candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When I had them for the first time,\Nthey just melted in my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that you enjoy them\Nas much as I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.69,0:04:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I got them from my big brother\Nwho knows all the trends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as good as you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.73,0:04:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ever want more,\NI can get you some whenever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.15,0:04:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's something that makes you smile,\Nit's a small price to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Koji, I'm so grateful for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Moments like this,\NI dream of them going on forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to save you from this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.68,0:04:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always saving me.\NPlease don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hardly enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to… to help you however I can,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever it takes,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,so that there's always\Na smile on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,\NYou know…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping beyond hope that I could get\Na new kimono to wear for school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I suppose\Nthe new semester is starting soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if that's the case, why don't you\Nbuy yourself two or three more then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Wow! Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.71,0:05:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My goodness, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.88,0:05:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You really do love spoiling\Nyour little girl, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The one I'm wearing now\Nis getting all worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you normally do at around noon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,\NOh…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the time I do my cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.69,0:05:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.86,0:05:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The day after tomorrow at noon,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:06:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like for you\Nto be ready and available. Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why bother with asking me at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm basically their servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no choice in the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My father knows that there's no reason\Nto tell me to be at our home tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I am always here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother? Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, have you seen Mother anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, let me think,\Nshe might be in the annex.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.33,0:06:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you two be going on an outing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm getting a new kimono\Nsince school is starting soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, would you look at that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear elder sister,\Nwhy don't you go wash your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,On your face!\NYou've got soot on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.73,0:07:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare try to welcome\Na guest into the house
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,with that mucky face of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already enough\Nof an embarrassment to our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,\NGood morning, Koji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Your clothes… You decided\Nto wear the Western-style today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They look so dashing on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.27,0:07:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, what's the occasion\Nfor your visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, right…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a discussion,\Nuh, with your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My father?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.13,0:08:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A souvenir snack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please share it with everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.34,0:08:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, um, I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Koji…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.52,0:08:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it have to be this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- Miss Miyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Master is calling for your attendance.\NYou should hurry over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants you\Nin the drawing room at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The day after tomorrow at noon,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like for you\Nto be ready and available. Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be pointless\Nto expect good…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,…when I know\Nit's going to be something bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Marriage arrangements with Koji…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get my hopes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My head already knows that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Miyo. May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's taking you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you please\Njust come in and sit already?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me be clear\Nabout our topic today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Marriage arrangements\Nwith the Tatsuishis's
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.07,0:10:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as our family's future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We've decided to take in Koji.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He will be our son-in-law\Nand our successor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The new head of the Saimori's.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The daughter who will support Koji\Nin marriage for our family's lineage…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-will be Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried so hard\Nto brace myself for this
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.43,0:10:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and I still wasn't ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,\NIt hurts… so terribly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I continue to hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I yearn to be accepted,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,to exist as one of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All I want is a bit of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.24,0:10:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo,\Nwe're sending you away to be married.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll wed into the Kudo family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:10:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You will become Kiyoka Kudo's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kudo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.50,0:11:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how lucky are you to get to\Nmarry the famous Mr. Kiyoka Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,For someone with no redeeming qualities,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,this arrangement is more than you deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.93,0:11:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so curious to see how many days\Nyou'll last in that man's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You will gather\Nall of your belongings at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.48,0:11:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That said, you will be leaving\Nfirst thing in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But, uh, Father--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.78,0:11:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all that concerns you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If you heard what I said,\Nthen go get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't cause a scene.\NYou will not embarrass us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-\N- Well, then, Koji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's plan the engagement ceremony…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The rain's not going to stop\Nany time soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There goes any chance\Nof putting the laundry up to dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it have to be me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me repeat myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You will marry into the Saimori's\Nwith Kaya as your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.64,0:12:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I possibly accept\Nall of that out of nowhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You say you want to save Miyo, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how you must do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinichi and I have sorted everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.15,0:12:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll marry Kazushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And she'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.36,0:12:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wanted, she'll be out of that home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,When you think about it, son,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.24,0:12:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't that what would be best\Nfor her life?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:12:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What about what she wants?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.62,0:13:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to be the one\Nwho ends up with Kaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything has been decided for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.21,0:13:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Your only task is\Nto obey silently for your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.27,0:13:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother's cherry blossom tree…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I could always come here\Nwhen I was sad or afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the only comfort\NI had in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't be able to come here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for always loving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Koji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I was totally worthless in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.47,0:13:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,\NI couldn't do anything for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:13:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Koji!\NPlease don't apologize for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.47,0:14:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It was luck.\NAnd mine just so happened to be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that!\NIt's not about luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.93,0:14:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I may find happiness\Nwith the family I marry into.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.32,0:14:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not concerned one way or the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you really don't resent me for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I resent you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've distanced myself\Nfrom any sort of feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I only ever wanted to save you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to spend all of our days\Nhappy together like when we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.71,0:14:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-I wanted us to be--\N- Oh, Koji?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you two talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I… It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.34,0:14:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Then come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- Koji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyo,\Nmay I open the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The Master said that\Nhe would like you to have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.93,0:15:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a new kimono for tomorrow\Nfor when you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that you should arrive in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My father said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're to wear it\Nto your new home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please listen to me, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.77,0:15:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyoka Kudo is rumored\Nto be a ruthless, cold-hearted man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He has already had fiancées\Nand they all left him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.36,0:15:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So be cautious, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. Thank you for your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all you're taking?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All of the mementos from my mother\Nwere thrown out long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.63,0:16:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing else to bring but this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. This place hasn't been kind to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this. I hope it will help you\Nwith your journey tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.68,0:16:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyo…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care and safe journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This kimono is so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way it would ever look good\Non someone like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. I have no home to return to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My whole world was here,\Nand all of my memories…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the right way?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the head of the Kudo family\Nreally live in this forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.16,0:20:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,His home is more modest than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.68,0:20:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,KUDO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we here for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, nice to meet you.\NMy name is Miyo Saimori.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.10,0:20:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here because of\Nthe marriage arrangement
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.61,0:20:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,my family made with one Mr. Kiyoka Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.19,0:20:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Miss Saimori.\NI was wondering when you'd arrive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.57,0:20:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You may call me Yurie.\NI am a servant in the Kudo home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard some chatter about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come in and make yourself at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.55,0:20:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The Young Master should be\Nin the study.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.34,0:20:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You can settle in later,\Nso why don't I take you to him right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Miyo Saimori.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.62,0:21:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for taking me into your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How long do you intend\Nto stay that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.39,0:21:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.92,0:21:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask for an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.89,0:21:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then, please raise your head\Nwhenever you feel ready to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh… oh, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.02,0:21:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,From the moment I saw him,\NI felt something shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What was once a dark space in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,has a sliver of light, a flower…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.49,0:21:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,so small, blossoming through the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.42,0:22:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kiyoka Kudo, head of the Kudo's.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.88,0:22:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful person!
